    "name": "Mesh convergence study — non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw FEA model",
    "description": "A systematic mesh refinement study was performed on the non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw FEA model to quantify discretization error. Five mesh densities were evaluated (element edge lengths ranging from 1.0 mm to 0.125 mm at the screw-rod interface). The Grid Convergence Index (GCI) was computed for construct stiffness and yield force QoIs. The study confirmed asymptotic convergence with GCI < 1.2% for both QoIs at the selected production mesh density of 0.25 mm. This activity was conducted prior to the validation comparison and is referenced in the discretization error credibility factor assessment.",
    "activityType": "MeshConvergenceStudy",
